OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772633478
OL,3,CFootball fan banned after headbutting
OL,4,Csteward and entering pitch
OL,6,FA football fan who headbutted a
OL,7,Fsteward and entered the pitch during a
OL,8,FReading FC match has been banned from
OL,9,Fattending matches for three years.
OL,11,FBrandon Bashforth, 28, of High Street
OL,12,Fin Grimethorpe, near Barnsley,
OL,13,Fattempted to reach the home
OL,14,Fsupporters' section during the League
OL,15,FOne game between Reading and Barnsley
OL,16,Fon Saturday 24 January 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
