PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772633478
OL,3,CFootball fan banned after headbutting
OL,4,Csteward and entering pitch
OL,6,FA steward at Reading's Select Car
OL,7,FLeasing Stadium tried to stop him, but
OL,8,FBashforth pushed him and headbutted
OL,9,Fhim in the face, causing minor
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FBashforth was arrested on the day of
OL,13,Fthe match and charged the following
OL,14,Fday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
