PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772633478
OL,3,CFootball fan banned after headbutting
OL,4,Csteward and entering pitch
OL,6,FBashforth pleaded guilty to assault by
OL,7,Fbeating, entering the playing area of
OL,8,Fa football pitch, and using
OL,9,Fthreatening words and behaviour likely
OL,10,Fto cause harassment, alarm or distress
OL,11,Fin a hearing at Reading Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt on Wednesday 25 February 2026.
OL,14,FAs well as the threeyear football
OL,15,Fbanning order, Bashforth was given a
OL,16,F#600 fine for assault and a #100 fine
OL,17,Ffor entering the pitch.
OL,19,FBashforth was also ordered to pay #200
OL,20,Fin victim compensation and #85 in
OL,21,Fcosts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
