PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772633478
OL,3,CFootball fan banned after headbutting
OL,4,Csteward and entering pitch
OL,6,FDedicated Football Officer PC Steve
OL,7,FMountain said: "Violence towards
OL,8,Fstewards, staff or supporters will
OL,9,Fnever be tolerated.
OL,11,F"This banning order sends a clear
OL,12,Fmessage that those who choose to
OL,13,Finvolve themselves in disorder at
OL,14,Ffootball matches will face significant
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@oD@POU
