PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772633478
OL,3,CFootball fan banned after headbutting
OL,4,Csteward and entering pitch
OL,6,F"A football banning order will prevent
OL,7,FBashforth from attending regulated
OL,8,Ffootball matches across the UK and can
OL,9,Falso include restrictions on travel,
OL,10,Fparticularly during international
OL,11,Ffixtures.
OL,13,F"They are a powerful tool that helps
OL,14,Fprotect fans, staff and the wider
OL,15,Fcommunity by keeping those intent on
OL,16,Fcausing trouble away from our
OL,17,Fstadiums."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
