OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772633478
OL,3,CFootball fan banned after headbutting
OL,4,Csteward and entering pitch
OL,6,F"Football should be a safe and
OL,7,Fenjoyable environment for everyone,
OL,8,Fand we will continue working with
OL,9,Fclubs to identify offenders and take
OL,10,Frobust action against them."
